                Mr. Jay
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-90f9f9e9-97e9-4665-9332-9b75a7af15f9" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
               data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
               data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1949-05-09/debates/1ca0a70c-810e-4031-b081-45b3c6bdda3e/ProfitsAndCapitalIssues#contribution-90f9f9e9-97e9-4665-9332-9b75a7af15f9">
